---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { u } from '../../lib/url';
import SectionBreath from '../../components/SectionBreath.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Thorn"
  description="Three services: digitalisation consultancy, custom software and integrations, data platforms and insights. Plain pricing, mapped to Romanian procurement thresholds."
  lang="en"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="surface-light pt-12 md:pt-20 pb-16 md:pb-24">
    <div class="container-page">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-y-8 md:gap-x-10">
        <div class="md:col-span-9">
          <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-8 md:mb-10">
            <span class="font-mono">001</span>
            <span class="mx-3 text-ink-300">·</span>
            Services
          </div>
          <h1 class="font-sans font-medium text-display-1 text-ink-900 hang tracking-tight">
            Three services.<br/>
            <span class="text-ink-400">Each priced on its own.</span>
          </h1>
        </div>

        <aside class="md:col-span-3 md:pt-32 md:border-l md:border-forest-100 md:pl-6">
          <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-3">Format</div>
          <div class="font-mono tabular text-ink-900 text-body-sm mb-6">Fixed fee</div>

          <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-3">Procurement</div>
          <div class="text-ink-900 text-body-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            SEAP-mapped<br/>
            DUAE-ready
          </div>

          <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-3">Discovery</div>
          <div class="text-ink-900 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
            Paid, not free
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 md:mt-16 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-body-lg text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
          We don't bundle. Most engagements start with the consultancy assessment because it forces clarity before money moves. From there, the work that needs building gets built, and the data that needs surfacing gets surfaced.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 01 — Consultancy -->
  <section id="consultancy" class="surface-medium section">
    <div class="container-page">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <div class="step-numeral-lg mb-6">01</div>
          <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-3">Consultancy</div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-display-3 text-ink-900 leading-tight tracking-tight mb-5">
            Digitalisation<br/>assessment
          </h2>
          <p class="text-ink-600 text-body leading-relaxed">
            A written roadmap your council or board can act on. One to two weeks of work. Fixed deliverable, fixed fee.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">

          <div class="card-secondary">
            <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-4">What you get</div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-ink-800 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-forest-400 mt-2">·</span><span>On-site assessment, one to three days, covering current systems, data flows and bottlenecks</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-forest-400 mt-2">·</span><span>Mapping of funding lines you currently qualify for: PNRR Component 7, Regional Programme Nord-Vest, DigiLocal, NIS2 compliance grants</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-forest-400 mt-2">·</span><span>A prioritised list of three to seven concrete interventions, costed against procurement thresholds</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-forest-400 mt-2">·</span><span>A 15 to 25 page written report decision-makers can review without us in the room</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-forest-400 mt-2">·</span><span>One follow-up working session to walk decision-makers through findings</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card-secondary">
            <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-4">Pricing</div>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono tabular text-2xl text-ink-900 mb-1">8K</div>
                <div class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-2">RON</div>
                <div class="text-body-sm text-ink-700 leading-snug">Small commune,<br/>single-system focus</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono tabular text-2xl text-ink-900 mb-1">20–25K</div>
                <div class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-2">RON</div>
                <div class="text-body-sm text-ink-700 leading-snug">Town,<br/>typical scope</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono tabular text-2xl text-ink-900 mb-1">40K</div>
                <div class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-2">RON</div>
                <div class="text-body-sm text-ink-700 leading-snug">County-level,<br/>multiple systems</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-forest-100 text-body-sm text-ink-500 leading-relaxed">
              Sits within the Achiziție Directă threshold (up to 270,120 RON). Single procurement, no fragmentation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card-secondary">
            <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-4">What we don't do here</div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-ink-800 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-rust-400 mt-2">·</span><span>We don't write grant applications you've already decided on without independent review</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-rust-400 mt-2">·</span><span>We don't certify the work of another consultancy</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-rust-400 mt-2">·</span><span>We don't deliver a deck. We deliver a written document with named responsibilities and timelines</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionBreath label="Build phase" tone="light" />

  <!-- 02 — Software -->
  <section id="software" class="surface-light section">
    <div class="container-page">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <div class="step-numeral-lg mb-6">02</div>
          <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-3">Software</div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-display-3 text-ink-900 leading-tight tracking-tight mb-5">
            Custom software<br/>& integrations
          </h2>
          <p class="text-ink-600 text-body leading-relaxed">
            Modules that close real operational gaps. Built on open standards. Maintained as part of the engagement.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
          <div class="card-secondary">
            <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-4">Where we focus</div>
            <dl class="space-y-5 text-body-sm">
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[160px,1fr] gap-3 sm:gap-6">
                <dt class="text-forest-800 font-medium">Public-sector modules</dt>
                <dd class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">Debt collection (executări silite), equipment & fleet (utilaje), funding tracker. Designed to slot alongside Regista, Sobis, Avansis without ripping them out.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[160px,1fr] gap-3 sm:gap-6">
                <dt class="text-forest-800 font-medium">Integrations</dt>
                <dd class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">ANAF (SPV, PatrimVen), SEAP, ERP and accounting platforms, document management, GIS systems.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[160px,1fr] gap-3 sm:gap-6">
                <dt class="text-forest-800 font-medium">Web applications</dt>
                <dd class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">Internal tools, citizen-facing portals, dashboards. Built for maintainability, not novelty.</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="card-secondary">
            <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-4">Pricing & procurement</div>
            <dl class="space-y-5">
              <div class="border-l-2 border-forest-200 pl-5">
                <dt class="text-body-sm font-medium text-forest-800 mb-1">Module licence + setup</dt>
                <dd class="font-mono tabular text-xl text-ink-900 mb-2">15K — 130K RON</dd>
                <p class="text-body-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Single-module (small commune) to multi-module (mid-sized city). Fits Ofertă Unică or Achiziție Directă.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-l-2 border-forest-200 pl-5">
                <dt class="text-body-sm font-medium text-forest-800 mb-1">Custom build</dt>
                <dd class="font-mono tabular text-xl text-ink-900 mb-2">40K — 250K RON</dd>
                <p class="text-body-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Focused integration to multi-system delivery. Mapped to the right SEAP procedure for the right scope.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-l-2 border-forest-200 pl-5">
                <dt class="text-body-sm font-medium text-forest-800 mb-1">Recurring maintenance</dt>
                <dd class="font-mono tabular text-xl text-ink-900 mb-2">3.5K — 6K RON / mo</dd>
                <p class="text-body-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Per primărie. Hosting, security updates, regulatory alignment, business-hours support, two minor feature additions per quarter.</p>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="card-secondary">
            <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-4">Open standards, your data stays yours</div>
            <p class="text-ink-700 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
              Public-sector deployments run on Romanian infrastructure (Romarg or ClausWeb for the data layer, compute scaled on demand). Open formats, exportable schemas, no vendor lock-in clauses. If you ever want to migrate away, we hand you everything that's yours.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 03 — Data -->
  <section id="data" class="surface-dark section">
    <div class="container-page">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <div class="step-numeral-lg mb-6">03</div>
          <div class="eyebrow text-forest-300 mb-3">Data</div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-display-3 text-cream-50 leading-tight tracking-tight mb-5">
            Data platforms<br/>& insights
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cream-100/70 text-body leading-relaxed">
            The reporting and analytics layer that turns operational data into management decisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
          <div class="card-secondary">
            <div class="eyebrow text-forest-300 mb-4">What we deliver</div>
            <dl class="space-y-5 text-body-sm">
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[180px,1fr] gap-3 sm:gap-6">
                <dt class="text-forest-300 font-medium">Platform foundation</dt>
                <dd class="text-cream-100/80 leading-relaxed">Ingestion from your operational systems, a single trusted layer for reporting, governance built in from day one.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[180px,1fr] gap-3 sm:gap-6">
                <dt class="text-forest-300 font-medium">Dashboards that get used</dt>
                <dd class="text-cream-100/80 leading-relaxed">Built with the people who need them, not for them. Two or three core views, refreshed nightly, that answer questions you actually ask in meetings.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[180px,1fr] gap-3 sm:gap-6">
                <dt class="text-forest-300 font-medium">Targeted analytics</dt>
                <dd class="text-cream-100/80 leading-relaxed">Forecasting, anomaly detection, segmentation. We start from a business question and work backwards.</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="card-secondary">
            <div class="eyebrow text-forest-300 mb-4">Pricing</div>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono tabular text-2xl text-cream-50 mb-1">€8K</div>
                <div class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-forest-400 mb-2">From</div>
                <div class="text-body-sm text-cream-100/70 leading-snug">Single-source<br/>dashboard pilot</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono tabular text-2xl text-cream-50 mb-1">€60K</div>
                <div class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-forest-400 mb-2">Up to</div>
                <div class="text-body-sm text-cream-100/70 leading-snug">Multi-source platform<br/>with governance + 3-5 dashboards</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-forest-700 text-body-sm text-cream-100/60 leading-relaxed">
              For private-sector clients no SEAP thresholds apply. For public-sector clients we map the same scope to the appropriate procurement procedure.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="surface-light section">
    <div class="container-page text-center">
      <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-6">004</div>
      <h2 class="font-sans font-medium text-display-2 text-ink-900 leading-tight mb-10 hang max-w-2xl mx-auto tracking-tight">
        Not sure which service fits?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body-lg text-ink-700 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Tell us the problem in plain language. We'll tell you what we'd start with, what we wouldn't, and what it would cost.
      </p>
      <a href={u('/en/contact')} class="btn-primary">
        Start a conversation
        <svg class="btn-arrow" width="14" height="10" viewBox="0 0 14 10" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M0 5h12M8 1l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
